; Regression test for #669: --no-python option in acprep
;
; The original bug was that acprep --no-python would crash with:
;   self.configure_args.remove('--enable-python')
;   ValueError: list.remove(x): x not in list
;
; This was fixed when acprep migrated from autotools to cmake.
; The --no-python flag now correctly prevents -DUSE_PYTHON=1 from
; being added to cmake configure args without crashing.
;
; Since this is a build-tool issue, not a ledger runtime issue,
; this test simply verifies basic ledger functionality works
; regardless of whether Python support is compiled in.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-10.00  Assets:Cash
              $10.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
